Sheeghra
========

Sheeghra is a mended version of Indic font 'Raghu' series. Raghu series is nice
OpenType font for languages in India, but unfortunately the fonts seem to be
corrupted and some of them are rejected by UniScribe. The aim of this project
is to fix the corrupted OpenType tables.

Raghu series is available under GPL v2 at:
http://www.cdacmumbai.in/projects/indix/n_download.shtml
